wiki.summary: “REALLY” challenges you to prove your love or else you’re gonna lose them. The song pairs modern American hip-hop elements with a smooth bass and tropical samples to deliver a summery vibe. The track is written by Danny Chung and Teddy Park and produced by choice37. This the third track on BLACKPINK’s first mini-album, SQUARE UP. The girl group attended KBS Cool FM’s radio show, Volume Up, to promote their new mini-album. Read more on Last.fm.
